dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Also covers Wales. "Supplement to the National Geographic, October 1979, page 442A, vol. 156, no. 4--British Isles." Includes text, historical notes, and col. ill. Insets: England in the Eighth century.--Henry II's empires 1154-1189.--Shetland Islands (Zetland). On verso: British Isles.
